Description:
   Charter Challenge is the Warden's battlefield provocation technique. The
   warrior issues a formal combat declaration that compels nearby enemies to
   redirect their attention toward them. Targeted opponents are taunted into
   focusing their attacks on the Warden rather than allies.

   In addition to redirecting aggression, Charter Challenge temporarily lowers
   the target's morale and combat efficiency, as the challenge undermines their
   confidence and forces them into a reactive stance. It is an essential tool
   for Wardens filling a protective role in group combat, enabling them to
   shield weaker party members by drawing enemy focus.
